# This repo only tracks the ui/ app. Everything else at this level is either a
# separate sibling git repo (pod-dapp-ports, coti-contracts, pod-mpc-lib, etc. —
# used for local devnet tooling, each with its own remote/history) or local
# state that should never be committed (.env holds private key material).
/*
!/.gitignore
!/README.md
!/ui
!/.github
